{"tid":729192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣 畢業生近4成有意海外發展:「大陸成首選」","createTime":"2018-07-04T10:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T13:32:55.000Z","uid":53060,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"51ccf98476a45e29f2ddb3f0a5097c50b65cf329","tid":729192,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180610/photo/bkncn-20180610104217802-0610_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180610111306\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180610%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180610104217802-0610_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180610111306&h=7d665034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣人力公司調查發現，大陸成為畢業生到海外工作的首選。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n台灣經濟不景，加上大陸陸續推出優待政策，令<span style=\"color: red;\">不少台灣人都轉到大陸發展</span>。台灣有人力資源公司近日進行抽樣調查，訪問了1138名應屆大學畢業生，發現近4成人有意願到海外工作，當中以想去大陸的最多。專家認為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大陸對台生來說，勝在沒有語言門檻、文化障礙</strong></span>，加上各種惠台措施，故較具吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n據「1111人力銀行」的調查顯示，受訪的應屆畢業生中，有38%<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有意到海外工作，當中62.53%選擇大陸</span></strong></span>，其次為美加地區、日本，考慮原因包括有較好的薪酬水平、能獲得國際經驗，以及建立海外人脈等。這批畢業生期望獲得的薪酬，平均為57445元新台幣（約15315港元），是打算留台者的1.76倍。<br />\n<br />\n該公司負責人李大華指，台灣物價雖相對平穩，但薪酬水平相對低；大陸的薪資雖然不會高出太多，但比起美加、日本、紐澳來說，兩岸在語言、文化上較為接近，加上大陸推出對台31項措施及創業基地等優惠政策，對台灣年輕人明顯較過往友善。"},{"pid":"ddd30f682ac87a1f1c244d70f4150734e134e541","tid":729192,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"合理，台灣無機會"},{"pid":"2af54d27db5e956899fd7a3c2716649ff2e25dde","tid":729192,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"台灣搞本土搞到啲精英走晒番大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0e576137bb015c9a66a533cc3acbc3ac7c5bf5","tid":729192,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"台灣人工低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8b7f16ccf81ed36639b91b9affb899c06d62f4","tid":729192,"uid":191701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"做黨內應"},{"pid":"dc17d6f4590b36e648b8c60adb0ff08eb022a97a","tid":729192,"uid":165377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:53:52.000Z","msg":"唔識英文咪得大陸揀"},{"pid":"4cdf78b9694f80f16eadbb14f619686ab1c58173","tid":729192,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"台灣年經一代被染紅了"},{"pid":"f5514b46433a6ef32c4c7135fb6c4fa81e443ae0","tid":729192,"uid":59192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc17d6f4590b36e648b8c60adb0ff08eb022a97a","tid":729192,"uid":165377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:53:52.000Z","msg":"唔識英文咪得大陸揀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"識英文既話有咩地方揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64335fbec12c20fff3898d1664e158ffc2d0137","tid":729192,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"這批<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>畢業生期望獲得的薪酬，平均為57445元新台幣（約15315港元）</strong></span>，是打算留台者的1.76倍。"},{"pid":"8e67b6a747cd72d8459682fd7e8cc98831bf71b3","tid":729192,"uid":72943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"係香港做零售仲高人工過係台灣畢業打份工"},{"pid":"26f87500132bfaed8f5f939106f1cd7b1ad0726f","tid":729192,"uid":13953,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"你估大陸人會用$15000<br />\n請MIT/Harvard/Oxbridge 海歸精英加自己人<br />\n定台灣野雞大學畢業既冇腦台仔"},{"pid":"f5a42013380cc78b2d693748177d9042b0ccfa85","tid":729192,"uid":27915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"台仔咁廢，除咗大陸都好難有地方可以去發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feda944308bc1305f60f375f65b549fe9dd53033","tid":729192,"uid":58335,"like":0,"di