07836442017793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fcaojitw%2Fstatus%2F1011807836442017793&d=hcKOE3i8VJxvkOAuUfaprdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0c550115\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/caojitw/status/1011807836442017793</a>"},{"pid":"b518ee8666c9ec3addac7812d9ff58bf0628d4b1","tid":729192,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"讀唔到電機，資工，理工科係台灣真係食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇能力又想高人工？我諗除左香港都冇咩地方可以做到。大陸就業環境都唔好，唔好睇到大陸咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7389a27e025a22b67cd2e7541f89c9f1893a29","tid":729192,"uid":154937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"之前有睇過專題節目<br />\n話班台灣學生一畢業<br />\n就可以申請研發資金<br />\n而且唔使佢地還<br />\n大概有20萬人民幣<br />\n一句講曬 <br />\n用錢籠絡人心啫"},{"pid":"cb702431eb8f48493773871f9b9a2018f52e8688","tid":729192,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f87500132bfaed8f5f939106f1cd7b1ad0726f","tid":729192,"uid":13953,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"你估大陸人會用$15000<br />\n請MIT/Harvard/Oxbridge 海歸精英加自己人<br />\n定台灣野雞大學畢業既冇腦台仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"平均月薪22000台幣既畢業生  諗住去大陸就有5皮幾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人返大陸都要捱低薪啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e090bbef6b8dbd83212b0c6dd61a067e93a13f59","tid":729192,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過, 台灣人可以利用呢個機會, 滲透中國??<br />\n<br />\n即係 台灣人去大陸工作, 可以向 同事 宣傳民主, 自由 既理念<br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n「我地台灣人可以屌鳩蔡英文, 你地可唔可以屌鳩習近平??」<br />\n「我地台灣人可以上youtube, 你地得唔得??」<br />\n<br />\n然後將民主, 自由既理念傳開去, 最終令中國革命"},{"pid":"59c2638e0faf5bdf95da5a8fdf9ae98cfcb07f64","tid":729192,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b